Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.comp

Class CompiledMapping<E extends Expression>

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.comp.CompiledMapping<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of expression this mapping will return
All Implemented Interfaces:
Logical, Simplifiable, Typed, Mapping<E>, Serializable, Comparable<Logical>
public class CompiledMapping<E extends Expression> extends Object implements Mapping<E>
A compiled mapping is a mapping whose get method only accepts ground characters and which always returns ground expressions.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
